
#require no-eden


  $ configure modern
  $ setconfig format.use-eager-repo=True

  $ newrepo e1
  $ drawdag << 'EOS'
  > E  # bookmark master = E
  > |
  > D
  > |
  > C  # bookmark stable = C
  > |
  > B
  > |
  > A
  > EOS

Read from the repo

  $ hg log -pr $E
  commit:      9bc730a19041
  bookmark:    master
  user:        test
  date:        Thu Jan 01 00:00:00 1970 +0000
  summary:     E
  
  diff -r f585351a92f8 -r 9bc730a19041 E
