  +++ b/E	Thu Jan 01 00:00:00 1970 +0000
  @@ -0,0 +1,1 @@
  +E
  \ No newline at end of file

  $ hg bookmarks
     master                    9bc730a19041
     stable                    26805aba1e60

Bookmarks

  $ hg book -d stable
  $ hg book stable -r $B
  $ hg bookmarks
